Package: RCandy
Title: RCandy:  an R package for rapid visualisation of homologous recombination 
       events in bacterial genomes
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Chrispin",
           family = "Chaguza",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "Chrispin.Chaguza@gmail.com"),
           person(given = "Gerry",
           family = "Tonkin-Hill",
           role = c("aut"),
           email = "gt4@sanger.ac.uk"))
Description: Plots a phylogenetic tree in context of taxon
    metadata and recombination events identified by Gubbins (Croucher et
    al. PMID: 25414349) and BRATNextGen (Marttinen et al. PMID: 22064866).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/ChrispinChaguza/RCandy/
BugReports: https://github.com/ChrispinChaguza/RCandy/issues
